      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 18 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 18 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：幹父之蠱，有子考，无咎，厲終吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows (a son) dealing with the troubles caused by his father. If he be an (able) son, the father will escape the blame of having erred. The position is perilous, but there will be good fortune in the end.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
