      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：幹母之蠱，不可貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows (a son) dealing with the troubles caused by his mother. He should not (carry) his firm correctness (to the utmost).</seg>
      </tuv>
