      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：幹父之蠱，小有悔，无大咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows (a son) dealing with the troubles caused by his father. There may be some small occasion for repentance, but there will not be any great error.</seg>
